        "Id": "46acc0c1-a05d-4256-8fff-67d8156e6e36",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Crows Network #1",
        "Location": "LOCATION_MUMBAI",
        "PublicId": "113215512534",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Mumbai/scene_mongoose.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 332eb76d-8c99-45c0-9cc1-6801e6915396).Image",
        "Description": "An organized crime gang in Mumbai, the Crows, have taken their operations too far by controlling a monopoly on forge services in the city, and our client, the government, wants to send them a message. You have been ordered to take out three key members of the gang, plus the head of the forge that has been working with them. To add extra flair, the client asks that you use the Crows&apos; own weapon on them; the Beak Staff. Good luck.",
